title: Open Bar #51 - Indy 5 Disaster, Little Mermaid Backlash, The Flash Review
description:
Its another busy week at The Bar as Razorfist, Chris Gore, Echo Chamberlain, MauLer and myself cover the recent embarassment for Lucasfilm as professional critics slam Indiana Jones 5, the backlash and accusations swirling around The Little Mermaid "reimagining", and an advance review of The Flash courtesy of Chris Gore.
